---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="意见反馈 - 无碍e家">
  <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-morandi-text tracking-tight mb-3 animate-spring-fade">意见反馈</h1>
  <p class="text-morandi-muted mb-10 animate-spring-fade stagger-1">如有问题、建议或合作意向，欢迎与我们联系。</p>

  <div class="max-w-xl glass-strong rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-10 animate-spring-in stagger-2">
    <p class="text-morandi-muted mb-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      您可以通过以下方式提交反馈：点击下方按钮将打开您的默认邮箱，并自动填写主题。
    </p>
    <a
      href="mailto:?subject=【无碍e家】意见反馈&body=请在此处填写您的问题或建议："
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium text-white spring-btn"
      style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-morandi-accent), #8c7e6e);"
    >
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75"/></svg>
      通过邮件提交反馈
    </a>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-morandi-subtle">
      如需配置在线表单（如 Formspree），请将表单 action 替换为您的 Formspree 端点。
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
